p.d: Fairly Normal is a glimpse of some of the best riders intimacy; the place where they live, the people sharing their lives, their travels. Get to meet the women and men behind the athletes when they are not in the spotlight. An ideal opportunity to have a look at their career, to come back on the key moment of their lives or simply to enjoy a good session with them. A What Youth series directed with poetry and sensitivity, capturing moments of natural beauty.
